357
00:22:53,447 --> 00:22:56,678
What a drag, Anna, what a drag.

358
00:22:57,767 --> 00:22:59,883
I love these old theatres.

359
00:23:00,807 --> 00:23:02,399
They are like violins,

360
00:23:03,447 --> 00:23:05,199
