I live at the hospital.

459
00:29:37,247 --> 00:29:39,602
- I didn't know that.
- Don't pretend!

460
00:29:39,767 --> 00:29:41,962
I didn't know, I promise!

461
00:29:43,887 --> 00:29:45,605
For the sake of Anna.

462
00:29:46,047 --> 00:29:47,036
